{"tid":197820,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"窮人生仔 累人累己","createTime":"2017-04-12T06:32:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-13T10:02:32.000Z","uid":73139,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4aaf19db879c492a769a24ed4acf2510480ea324","tid":197820,"uid":73139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T06:32:33.000Z","msg":"點解父母親可以將自己嘅責任推卸得一乾二淨？<br />\n將自己應該要做嘅嘢 推俾你做<br />\n仲要好撚合理咁講 呢啲係你嘅責任<br />\n我真係屌你老尾<br />\n嬲到講唔到野<br />\n乜撚都係我自己搞掂嘅<br />\n我理鳩你做乜柒？<br />\n心情好撚低落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85d80839248398e8c639c7390d0c1c6ccbdb5966","tid":197820,"uid":88190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T08:34:22.000Z","msg":"發生咩事?<br />\n講黎聽下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce6a125fa9b9503ef0437f1289ec7dd944deb316","tid":197820,"uid":73139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T10:06:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>發生咩事?<br />\n講黎聽下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我中六畢業冇耐 今年想讀毅進 <br />\n學費我屋企人想我自己搞掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0da5ec13d32dcb975ba73fff2b643f9c41cc7a95","tid":197820,"uid":73139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T10:09:35.000Z","msg":"平時已經冇問過屋企攞錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有時仲會幫手交下水電煤<br />\n我點樣一次過攞三皮幾出尼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n下年一整年讀書期間啲錢又要自己搞掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想死...<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab5710c9e36f28a0a4a0e931615fcd18e26db32f","tid":197820,"uid":14870,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T10:10:09.000Z","msg":"尼你老母"},{"pid":"28c6bf519abef8336482048eca237c72a1244d15","tid":197820,"uid":73139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T10:10:16.000Z","msg":"黎*<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"158a9e83b131a2e5eca60b00c67575185bd1d683","tid":197820,"uid":100120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T10:12:42.000Z","msg":"唔緊要喇 畢業之後去做狗<br />\n就還到架喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53497ce424d9449c0a2a46d19b743ef39682fdd5","tid":197820,"uid":73139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T10:14:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔緊要喇 畢業之後去做狗<br />\n就還到架喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點撚解可以生撚完我出黎之後就咩都唔撚理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49d82e605e9f71d438f0c934579227c2079e7d27","tid":197820,"uid":73139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T10:15:04.000Z","msg":"呢個世界公平咩！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11508d5b939f5bede7111316177ea8b4fa8b3bf2","tid":197820,"uid":55458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T10:16:56.000Z","msg":"讀得偽進都叫畢業？"},{"pid":"6cd731fc7d0ce9b08d73b0d26762172f365c4d98","tid":197820,"uid":73139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T10:20:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>讀得偽進都叫畢業？</blockquote><br />\n細個因為啲事所以成績未如理想<br />\n不過我冇後悔到"},{"pid":"8c89ea3a901531531781ddce3ea87c000576370f","tid":197820,"uid":14870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T10:22:23.000Z","msg":"讀書錢自己比有幾撚出奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d21a61d9fe7ff2e24021813253a855ceeb38a44a","tid":197820,"uid":100120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T10:22:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔緊要喇 畢業之後去做狗<br />\n就還到架喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點撚解可以生撚完我出黎之後就咩都唔撚理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n邊個比飯你食?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b146128cae59357925556de288d5052abb0c59c","tid":197820,"uid":104432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T10:25:30.000Z","msg":"唔考慮直接搵d會資助埋你返學既工？"},{"pid":"3632060219e1b9b0d0870c83f99eef62cc41a352","tid":197820,"uid":17213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T10:27:16.000Z","msg":"假膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無錢咪問政府借低息貸款<br />\n之後慢慢攤開還"},{"pid":"3dadba2850b9b49bffca9d880a402a5ecc1e9a38","tid":197820,"uid":73139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T10:28:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>讀書錢自己比有幾撚出奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你中學一畢業就自己比錢上大學？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ea2eae22922624247590c89a186a86583ec5ade","tid":197820,"uid":73139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T10:28:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔緊要喇 畢業之後去做狗<br />\n就還到架喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點撚解可以生撚完我出黎之後就咩都唔撚理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n邊個比飯你食?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都唔撚記得屋企有幾耐未煮過飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00c5ad80efd6cf8600ed73c4d0a1611b71d704a4","tid":197820,"uid":73139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T10:30:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔考慮直接搵d會資助埋你返學既工？</blockquote><br />\n自己有份不錯嘅工作返緊"},{"pid":"5d83c2205d12c3c13cf6c38527853f9e1108c88b","tid":197820,"uid":46200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T10:31:24.000Z","msg":"窮人生仔，本身係仆街<br />\n<br />\n但你讀唔成書<br />\n點解仲要讀<br />\n好人好者，點會要讀毅進<br />\n<br />\n怪你老豆老母嘅時候<br />\n有冇諗過你連讀書咁簡單嘅嘢都做唔好<br />\n有得免費讀個陣又唔讀<br />\n又話有原因，又唔講出嚟<br />\n係都要用幾皮野買個垃圾証書<br />\n<br />\n你咁撚樣，你父母有錢到曉飛你都係柒架啦"},{"pid":"17ffe553d0cfefbe861dcabdb8383394012c725b","tid":197820,"uid":73139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T10:31:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>假膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無錢咪問政府借低息貸款<br />\n之後慢慢攤開還</blockquote><br />\n咁而家嘅問題就係佢哋有但唔肯比 點解我要去貸款呢？你好撚鍾意問人借錢？"},{"pid":"45f56b834e64d36f132860ae55b1d97153e02c55","tid":197820,"uid":22574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T10:34:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>假膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無錢咪問政府借低息貸款<br />\n之後慢慢攤開還</blockquote><br />\n咁而家嘅問題就係佢哋有但唔肯比 點解我要去貸款呢？你好撚鍾意問人借錢？</blockquote><br />\n佢唔肯比你都要讀㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔夠錢咪又係要借"},{"pid":"ca31fa1f51b7abaf945c01af7cf4972f0a79f700","tid":197820,"uid":73139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T10:35:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>窮人生仔，本身係仆街<br />\n<br />\n但你讀唔成書<br />\n點解仲要讀<br />\n好人好者，點會要讀毅進<br />\n<br />\n怪你老豆老母嘅時候<br />\n有冇諗過你連讀書咁簡單嘅嘢都做唔好<br />\n有得免費讀個陣又唔讀<br />\n又話有原因，又唔講出嚟<br />\n係都要用幾皮野買個垃圾証書<br />\n<br />\n你咁撚樣，你父母有錢到曉飛你都係柒架啦</blockquote><br />\n簡單？每個人成長嘅背景都唔同 有啲嘢唔係你有得揀 如果係因為我自己唔俾心機 讀唔成係我自己抵撚死 我讀毅進係因為我好想做消防"},{"pid":"c0969b59e138b8dbe32de703619bed8ebd234104","tid":197820,"uid":73139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T10:37:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>假膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無錢咪問政府借低息貸款<br />\n之後慢慢攤開還</blockquote><br />\n咁而家嘅問題就係佢哋有但唔肯比 點解我要去貸款呢？你好撚鍾意問人借錢？</blockquote><br />\n佢唔肯比你都要讀㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔夠錢咪又係要借</blockquote><br />\n最親嘅人都唔肯幫你 個下真係好撚灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68f4341979b7034963a62b5c0fdc5d31e35f2070","tid":197820,"uid":82125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T11:02:52.000Z","msg":"老豆老母讀到中三就算，跟住屋企收入唔多都仲生左2件出黎。<br />\n<br />\n到我18歲完左dse 升上去，一冇左&ldquo;免費教育&rdquo; 要交幾萬蚊學費時，兩老面都青埋，原來佢地諗住讀大專一蚊都唔駛比<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n鬼叫你地窮都仲生2件咩，生之前又唔諗清諗楚，過一日得一日，雖然你地3餐溫飽，有間公屋，但比過咩童年回憶比小朋友？"},{"pid":"01e01704f38af88a4a423d94793e41bdbb988fbe","tid":197820,"uid":14870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T11:03:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>讀書錢自己比有幾撚出奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你中學一畢業就自己比錢上大學？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我借錢囉 借足3年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}